            "custom_liquid": "{%- comment -%}\n  ============================================================\n  LOREN – סרגל תועלות (Benefit Pills)\n  ------------------------------------------------------------\n  מיקום: הדביקו בלוק Custom Liquid זה *מתחת לכפתור \"הוסף לעגלה\"*.\n  תגיות קטנות (pills) שהלקוח קולט במבט אחד, לפני הגלילה.\n  RTL, מותאם נייד ומחשב.\n  ============================================================\n{%- endcomment -%}\n\n<div class=\"loren-benefits\" dir=\"rtl\">\n  <ul class=\"loren-benefits__grid\">\n\n    <li class=\"loren-benefits__item\">\n      <span class=\"loren-benefits__ic\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.9\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 4 13C4 8 8 4 20 4c0 8-4 12-9 12z\"/><path d=\"M4 20c3-6 7-8.5 12-9.5\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n      100% טבעי\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"loren-benefits__item\">\n      <span class=\"loren-benefits__ic\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.9\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M8 3l4 2 4-2 4 3-2.5 2.7L16 8v12H8V8l-1.5.7L4 6z\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n      על הבגד, לא על העור\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"loren-benefits__item\">\n      <span class=\"loren-benefits__ic\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.9\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 3l7 3v5c0 4.5-3 8-7 10-4-2-7-5.5-7-10V6z\"/><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n      בטוח מגיל 0\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"loren-benefits__item\">\n      <span class=\"loren-benefits__ic\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.9\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/><path d=\"M12 7v5l3.5 2\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n      עד 8 שעות הגנה\n    </li>\n\n    <li